These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
House: cape-cod, farmhouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, jet-ski
1. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the jet-ski is the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| House   | farmhouse | cape-cod |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | tram   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, scientific
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, lizard
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | sports        |
| Pet      | guinea-pig  | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different games are played: canasta, go
There 2 different types of food: kale, mango
1. the person eating kale is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Game   | go    | canasta |
| Food   | kale | mango |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
City: hamburg, san-francisco
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, poppy
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| City   | hamburg      | san-francisco |
| Flower       | sunflower | poppy    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
